high_descs: Go to your right, around the table in front of you, to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Move slightly right, to the counter right of the sink.
Put the spatula back on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Return a washed spatula to a kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the stove top, then turn left and walk forward across the room to the spatula on the counter by the sink.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn right, walk slightly forward, then turn left towards the counter.
Put the spatula on the counter, in front of and to the left of the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spatula on a counter top.

high_descs: Make a left to walk around the kitchen island to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the spatula from the countertop.
Rinse the spatula in the kitchen sink.
Turn to face the countertop to the right of the sink.
Set the spatula down on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Wash a spatula from the countertop to put it back.
